+
+**Completed**: Add-Path NLRI parsing, EVPN withdraw, ExtComm/RT decode, BGP-LS NLRI scaffolding, RPKI RTR client scaffold, analytics rewrite (ZScore, HijackDetector, RouteLeakDetector, FlapScorer). 38 tests pass.
